Sharon Thomas https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sharon_Thomas 0 Sharon Thomas (born June 3, 1946) is an American actress. She is the wife of director Christopher Cain. Their three children are musician Roger Cain and actors Dean Cain and Krisinda Cain Schafer. Sharon_Thomas ( born June_3_,_1946 ) is an_American_actress .
